Day 8: SQL & Database Testing with ChatGPT
CRUD Operations
CRUD is one of the most common interview topics.
Operation	  SQL
Create	  INSERT
Read	  SELECT
Update	UPDATE
Delete	DELETE
_________________________________________
Database Validation for QA
Example:
Requirement:
User registers.
Validate:
SELECT * FROM Users
WHERE email='abc@test.com';
Check:
Email
Name
Created Date
Status
_____________________________________________
API + Database Validation
API:
POST /users
Returns:
201 Created

Backend validation:
SELECT * FROM Users
WHERE email='abc@test.com';

Compare:
API Response
Database Record
